Starting with inputs_pd_curved:

inputs_candice0 - straightened
inputs_candice1 - orient wave to travel in x-direction
inputs_candace2 - add shoulder
inputs_candace2s - change input to soft source
inputs_candace3 - turn metal to PEC layer
inputs_candace3a - parameterize by frequency, not wavelength
inputs_candace4 - length/time scale to match 2.5 micron dx/dy
